"contenuto. "

#: src/modules/multiple-authors/multiple-authors.php:1478
msgid ""
"With this shortcode you can display the author names or any profile field in "
"any part of the content."
msgstr ""
"Usando lo shortcode puoi visualizzare i nomi degli autori o un altro campo "
"del profilo in qualsiasi parte del contenuto."

#: src/modules/multiple-authors/multiple-authors.php:1547
msgid ""
"With this shortcode, you can show all the authors together in a single "
"display."
